The evidence with the title 'How can we, how should we, regulate hobby drones? - LA Times ' says Sep 20, 2015  ... Not too long ago , unmanned aircraft systems — better known as drones — were seen primarily as atool the military used to spy on bad guys in combat  ... Administration — the agency that regulates aircraft safety and the use of airspace — recognize the need to regulate drones operating in U.S. skies . 
